quran[20]{c,v,t}:
  26,20,( moose ne ) kahan ( haan ) woh harkat mujh se nagahan sarzad hui thi aur mein khata karon mein tha
  26,21,to jab mujhe tum se dar laga to tum mein se bhaag gaya. phir khuda ne mujh ko nabuwat وعلم bakhsha aur mujhe payghambaroon mein sekiya
  26,22,aur (kiya ) yahi ahsaan hai jo aap mujh par rakhtay hain ke aap ne bani Israel ko ghulam bana rakha hai
  26,23,firaon ne kaha ke tamam Jahan maalikkiya
  26,24,kaha ke asmano aur zameen aur jo kuch un dono mein hai sab ka maalik. bashart e kay tum logon ko yaqeen ho
  26,25,firaon ne apne ا aahali mawali se kaha kekiya tum suntay nahi
  26,26,( moose ne ) kaha ke tumhara aur tumahray pehlay baap dada ka maalik
  26,27,( firaon ne ) kaha ke ( yeh ) paighambar jo tumhari taraf bheja gaya hai bawla hai
  26,28,"moose ne kaha ke mashriq aur maghrib aur jo kuch un dono mein hai sab ka maalik, bashart e kay tum ko samajh ho"
  26,29,( firaon ne ) kaha ke agar tum ne mere siwa kisi aur ko mabood banaya to mein tumhe qaid kardoon ga
  26,30,( moose ne ) kaha khuwa mein aap ke paas roshan cheez lau ( yani moujza )
  26,31,firaon ne kaha agar sachey ho to usay lao ( dikhao )
  26,32,pas unhon ne apni laathi daali to woh isi waqt Sarih اasdaha ban gayi
  26,33,aur apna haath nikala to isi dam dekhnay walon ke liye safaid ( Buraq nazar anay laga )
  26,34,firaon ne apne gird ke sardaro se kaha ke yeh to kaamil fun jadugar hai
  26,35,chahta hai ke tum ko apne jaadoo ( ke zor ) se tumahray malik se nikaal day to tumharikiya raye hai ?
  26,36,unhon ne kaha ke usay aur is ke bhai ( ke baray ) mein kuch tawaquf kijiye aur shehron mein hrkare bhaij dijiye
  26,37,ke sab maahir gado garon ko ( jama karkay ) aap ke paas le ayen
  26,38,to jadugar aik muqarara din ki meyaad par jama hogaye
  26,39,aur logon se keh diya gaya ke tum ( sab ) ko ikhatay ho kar jana chahiye
